  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854350/extras/c506b2124cfc25d27b3b2db4f50c6075.avif?t=1769370312\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br>◆打败敌人获得不同品质的装备，红色和紫色最为稀有<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854350/extras/0b0754e424fa3bf39e467b1b3ccf8360.avif?t=1769370312\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br>◆装备拥有随机属性值和词条，其中技能词条非常重要，多数技能达到8级以上会有质的飞跃<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854350/extras/f2b44043ef29d9a777b9fc309395af71.avif?t=1769370312\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br>◆各种街边美食散落在场景各处，吃了它们可以永久增加角色属性<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854350/extras/77bfd31ffa7fc9a3d44ee41b44f95bc0.avif?t=1769370312\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br>◆卖废品赚到的钱没处花？可以购买家具或者装饰品，放置在家里，也可以增加角色属性<br><br><br><br>游戏交流Q群：966022565<br><br>B站：易远游戏",
